('RiddleMath', 4338, 'Math Riddles level up your IQ with a mix of logical puzzles. Challenge yourself with different levels of math games and stretch the limits of your mind. Brain games are prepared with an approach of an IQ test.', 'For Pc - Use your mouse to click on any of the available numbers Once selected click on an empty spot in the puzzle to place the number there For Mobile - Drag the number from the available list and drop it into the empty space', 'English');
