('retrohero the last stand', 4345, 'Enter a mythic pixel world where ancient guardians rise to protect their realm from invaders. As the chosen defender, you must face endless waves of aliens, ruthless robots, and demonic creatures seeking to conquer your land. Armed with mystical powers and legendary artifacts, every battle is a test of skill and survival. With vibrant retro pixel art, fast-paced action, and a clash of mythology and sci-fi, this game challenges you to adapt, crush enemies, and prove that the ancient spirit can withstand any external threat. The fate of the world rests in your hands.', 'left up right down a s', 'English'),
('Connect Em All', 4346, 'Play Connect Em All Online and Solve Colorful Dot Puzzles. Connect Em All is an exciting and addictive puzzle game that you can enjoy for free right in your browser. The goal is simple yet surprisingly challenging: connect all the dots of the same color to complete each level. It sounds easy at first, but as the puzzles grow in size and complexity, you will need clever thinking and careful planning to succeed.', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Guess Words Fast', 4347, 'Guess Words Fast challenges players to swiftly decipher words from clues provided. In this high-paced game, players race against time to identify words accurately, testing their vocabulary and cognitive skills. With each correct guess, players accumulate points, fostering a competitive spirit among participants. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.bestcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.bestcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt; The games dynamic nature keeps players engaged, as they strive to beat their own records or compete with friends and family.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Evolve Numbers', 4348, 'Merge tiles with identical numbers by sliding them across the board. When two tiles with the same number combine, they create a new tile with double the value. The goal is to reach the 2048 tile to win, but you can keep playing for an even higher score. Be careful not to run out of moves!', 'On PC Use the arrow keys Up Down Left Right to move the tiles On mobile devices Swipe your finger in the desired direction Up Down Left Right to move the tiles', 'English');
