('Sprunki Whooo', 4352, 'Face the funniest card puzzle ever in Sprunki Whooo. Together with the adorable Sprunki characters, youll figure out the right answer in a deck full of surprises! Choose a character as your target. Each round presents a weird or funny question. Constantly ask each other about the characteristics of the target and eliminate all the wrong ones. Finally, identify the target and arrest him. Win rounds to unlock more Sprunki cards and characters!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Alien Clicker Invaders', 4353, 'Alien Clicker Invaders is a thrilling action and reflex game where you face endless waves of alien invaders! Get ready to click like crazy as you defend Earth against enemy hordes and colossal bosses that will test your skills. Collect powerful power-ups, unlock upgrades, and evolve your attack strength to survive each new wave of destruction! Play alone or share your mission to protect the Earth with a friend playing on a mobile device!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Merge Animals game', 4354, 'Merge Animals is a very simple but addictive game where you have to touch 2 identical objects together to make them explode and go to the next level', 'Click or drag and drop animals anywhere on the screen to drop them on top of the animals of the same type and earn points 2 animals of the same type merge and turn into a bigger fruit in the position where they collide so you can blast the bears the bi', 'English'),
('Sausage Flip Free', 4355, 'In Sausage Flip Free, youre not just any sausage. You&amp;rsquo;re a daring, bouncy hero on a mission to overcome wild levels full of danger, timing, and precision! This action, casual game blends goofy fun with real skill challenges! Tap to launch your sausage with a perfect flip! Launch the sausage on the vine and keep moving to the next pot or shelf, etc. Use your perfect skills to master each tricky obstacle. Cross the finish line to win.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Match Factory', 4356, 'Welcome to Match Factory - the most relaxing and non-stop casual triple puzzle game. Step into a vibrant factory full of colorful items, and play the role of a master matcher. Match three identical items to clear them from the board, pack them up, and keep the factory running smoothly! Every level is uniquely designed with tricky layouts and challenges. Use power-ups that help you overcome difficult puzzles!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Drag Race X', 4357, 'Drag Race X is an adrenaline-pumping racing game where you test your skills on high-speed straight tracks. Game Features: Fast-paced 3D drag racing with realistic graphics. Daily challenges and global tournaments. Smooth controls for all types of players. Immersive sound and visual effects for maximum thrill. Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate Drag Race X champion', 'Mouse click or tap to play use vitesse', 'English'),
('Back To School: Uniforms Edition', 4358, 'Explore global fashion in Back to School: Uniforms Edition! This fun dress-up game lets you spin the wheel to unlock school uniforms from countries like Japan, the U.S., the U.K., India, France, and South Korea. Customize your character with stylish outfits, accessories, and hairstyles inspired by each culture. Dive into the diversity of school uniforms and become a fashion expert while having fun! Discover all seven uniform styles featured in this online dress-up game for girls and find your favorite. Have a blast!', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
