('Duo Adventures (Legacy of Traps)', 4360, 'This game was made by me and my friends (Vinh) :&amp;gt; (Design,story and coding...) If you enjoyed it, please leave a comment or support us by donating!!! Your support really motivates me and my friends to keep making games! Thank you so much for playing! ################################################################# About the Game This is a HARDCORE PUZZLE ADVENTURE GAME. Note: The game is designed for 2 players. You can play solo, but it might be pretty challenging!', 'Player 1 WASD Player 2 Arrow Keys Goal Collect enough coins and head to the door to escape', 'English'),
('Click_Crates', 4361, 'Step into the action in this fun and fast-paced 3D skill game! Your goal is simple: tap and destroy the crates before they disappear &amp;mdash; but stay sharp, the difficulty increases as you go! Test your reflexes across 3 difficulty levels: Easy, Normal, and Hard Improve your focus and reaction time Compete for the best score &amp;mdash; can you beat your high score? Optimized for desktop and mobile WebGL play Includes dynamic sound effects for better experience Perfect for casual players who love a challenge. Try it now and see how far you can go', 'Mouse Click ndash Destroy crates Menu Navigation ndash Use mouse to select difficulty retry or navigate menus Works on Desktop WebGL', 'English'),
('Veggie Slice', 4362, 'Veggie Slice is an arcade slicing game where you slice vegetables with precision and avoid deadly dynamites. Earn high scores by chaining perfect combos. The game features endless mode with progressive difficulty, combo bonuses, and special veggies that boost your score. Miss three veggies, and it&amp;rsquo;s game over! With colorful visuals and smooth mouse or touch controls, its a fun challenge for all ages on both desktop and mobile.', 'Mouse Click and drag Touch Swipe to slice', 'English'),
('TapSync Blocks', 4363, 'Get ready to test your timing and reflexes in TapSync Blocks! In this vibrant arcade challenge, your goal is to tap at just the right moment to match the moving color with the central block. Each correct match earns you points, but a single wrong move costs you a life. With only 3 lives per round, precision is key! As the game speeds up, can you keep your cool and maintain perfect sync?', 'Click at the time where matching block is around', 'English'),
('Sprunki Squid Gaming', 4364, 'In Squid Gaming, you must survive. Compete with your friend &amp;mdash; first, make it through the Green Light, Red Light game alive, and then beat your friend in the tug-of-war game. Remember, you have to reach the end of the game before time runs out. After that, challenge your friend again in the next game, where the best tug-of-war player wins before time runs out. A short but fun competitive game you can play with your friend. Play in two different modes with your friend and celebrate the winner.', 'Use the A and P keys to move Playable on both mobile and PC 2 different short game modes', 'English'),
('Linking Battle', 4365, 'You are a wizard. You will beat your enemies by linking elements in your brain. When 3 or more elements are linked, you can release your power. Hope you enjoy your trip.', 'Mouse', 'English'),
('Cosmic Clicker', 4366, 'Cosmic Clicker is a highly engaging and monetizable idle clicker game set in a vibrant, stylized cosmos. The core loop is simple and addictive: click celestial objects to earn points, spend them on strategic upgrades, and watch your score soar into the trillions. With deep progression systems including missions, achievements, permanent upgrades, and a prestige Rebirth mechanic, the game is built for long-term player retention.', 'Mouse', 'English'),
('Water Sort Legend', 4367, 'Water Sort Legend is a brain-teasing puzzle game with a twist of fun, coins, and challenge! Sort colored water into the right tubes &amp;mdash; test your logic, improve your IQ, and unlock new levels as you go! With over 150 handcrafted levels across Easy, Medium, and Hard difficulties, players will never run out of puzzles to solve. Features: Level Unlock System &amp;ndash; Beat a level to unlock the next! IQ Estimator &amp;ndash; Get a smartness score based on your moves! Coins &amp;amp; Currency System &amp;ndash; Earn coins for every win. Upgrade Shop &amp;ndash; Spend coins on helpful boosters: Extra Tube Coin Booster Color Helper Sound FX &amp;ndash; Clean sounds', 'Desktop Click on a tube to select it Click on another tube to pour the water if allowed Use your mouse to play ndash no keyboard needed Mobile Tap on a tube to select Tap on another tube to pour water Fully optimized for touch controls', 'English'),
('Pop the Bubbles: Relaxing', 4368, 'A simple and captivating game designed to help you unwind and escape the daily hustle. Pop colorful bubbles to soothing music and enjoy beautiful visuals. Perfect for stress relief and relaxation, with endless levels and a calming vibe. Minimal effort, maximum enjoyment &amp;ndash; the ideal way to relax. Launch now and immerse yourself in a world of tranquility and fun!', 'Find groups of bubbles of the same color Press 2 times to pop The more bubbles pop at a time the more points', 'English');
