('Cool Man Adventure', 4407, 'Hi there! It sounds like youre interested in playing Cool Man Adventure, To play, youll need to jump &amp;amp; run on platforms, avoid obstacles and fire gas , robo, gear ring , and defeat enemies. Dont forget to collect key along the way! The game has 10 levels for you to explore, so theres plenty of adventure to be had.', 'To control your character you can use the arrow keys on your keyboard Alternatively if youre playing on a mobile device you can tap the game screen icons to move your character around', 'English'),
