('Survival Rpg Island Escape', 4438, 'Do you want to have an exciting island survival adventure in Survival RPG: Island Escape? You will be the last survivor and on a mysterious island of pixels. Collect many resources and make tools.For example, water bottles are used to hold water, knives for defense, fruit for energy and so on.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
